mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record and Record Report", "As I See It", "What Are They Dancing?", "14th National Convention", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Overseas Dateline", "The "Computed Go To"", "Style Series: Tips on Standardization", "Ladies on the Square", "Round the Outside Ring", "Sets in Order Workshop", "Paging the Roundancers: Frank and Mary Robinson", "Caller of the Month: Jack Livingston", and "Experimental Lab: Loop the Loop".
